    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43160</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_010_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれが、時空戦士のひとり……だった
&lt;Klarth&gt;博士なんてな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Look at that... even though the renowned &lt;Klarth&gt; is an Eternal Hero he turned into that...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_010_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルゥ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruuu...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_010_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いんやー、くさかっただなぁ～。
ポケットの中にいても、匂ってきただど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At last I can get out~! The inside of that pocket smells horrible, kinda resembles someone ...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_010_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いくらなんでもちょっと飲み過ぎだよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whatever the case, we shouldn't think so much about it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_010_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、酔ってたからって
あんな言い方ないと思う……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, still! That's no way to talk to us...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43652</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_010_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだんだ。&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;をバカにするなんて許せねーだよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's ok &lt;Mel&gt;-&lt;Mel&gt;! I'll never forgive that stupid old man for anything he said!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_010_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>体中の穴という穴から酒が染み出てきて、
あんだけくせーんだよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If I had come out, I'd have stained all his body's holes! That's how far I'd go for you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_010_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>体中の穴という穴……！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All...his body's holes...!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
